title: [Wehnimer's, Courtyard]
description: A small courtyard is bordered on all sides by a high wooden wall.  Ivy covers much of it, the dark green leaves creating a dense cover which blocks out almost all of the noise from Wehnimer's busy streets.  Flagstones are set into a path passing under a lattice arch, which offers an avenue out of the picturesque enclosure.
location: the Garden Cottage, inside the frontier town of Wehnimer's Landing
